# Title: UAC Bypass Tools Using ComputerDefaults
# Author: Christian Burkard (Nextron Systems)
# Date: 2021-08-31
# Level: high
# Description: Detects tools such as UACMe used to bypass UAC with computerdefaults.exe (UACMe 59)
# MITRE Tactic: Privilege Escalation
# Tags: attack.privilege-escalation, attack.t1548.002
# Reference: https://github.com/SigmaHQ/sigma/blob/master/rules/windows/process_creation/proc_creation_win_uac_bypass_computerdefaults.yml

Image="C:\\Windows\\System32\\ComputerDefaults.exe" IntegrityLevel IN ("High", "System", "S-1-16-16384", "S-1-16-12288") NOT (ParentImage IN ("*:\\Windows\\System32*", "*:\\Program Files*"))